            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>(chop in one bunch for speed)</p><p>Wash then cut your<strong> pak choi</strong> in half, separating the <strong>white base</strong> and <strong>green tops</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Set aside the <strong>green tops</strong>, then chop the <strong>white bases</strong> into rough, large pieces</p><p>Discard the tough stalk</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1678178020951-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
