            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add most of the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>spring onion </strong>(save the rest for garnish!), the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>pak choi white bases</strong> and your <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> to the<strong> </strong>chicken and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1678178028865-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1678178028865-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1678178028865-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1678178028865-x1000.jpg",
