          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1678178028865-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>roasted peanuts</strong>, <strong>white</strong> <strong>miso paste</strong>, <strong>honey</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and a splash of <strong>boiled water</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min further or until the sauce has thickened</p><p>Meanwhile, drain the <strong>noodles</strong> and add to the pan, then stir through your <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame oil </strong>–<strong> </strong>these are your <strong>sesame noodles</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1678178032422-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1678178032422-x400.jpg",
