            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>pak choi green tops </strong>and cook for 30 secs further or until slightly wilted and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>honey miso & peanut chicken breast stir fry</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
