    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>honey miso & peanut chicken breast stir fry</strong> over the <strong>sesame</strong> <strong>noodles</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
